      "value": "<p>&gt;@Compendium[sfrpg.class-features.UVNOjH2ERlQjcGnU]{Zenith Revelation}</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl53_LabelName\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl07_LabelName\" style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\"><sub style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary);\"><img style=\"border: 1px solid var(--color-border-dark);\" src=\"systems/sfrpg/images/cup/gameplay/photon.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></sub><span style=\"font-family: var(--font-primary); font-size: var(--font-size-14);\">&nbsp;</span></span></span><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTalentsAll_ctl53_LabelName\">Photon Revelation<br /></span>When you&rsquo;re fully photon-attuned, you can invite creatures of fiery power to fight for you as a standard action. This functions as @Compendium[sfrpg.spells.rJ0acpj21GDJYaim]{Summon Creature} with a spell level equal to one-third your solarian level. You select which four creatures you can summon each time you gain a solarian level, and they must all be fire creatures. The natural attacks of creatures you summon with this ability have the @Compendium[sfrpg.equipment.8jS8wtBmw01lQU7D]{Limning} weapon fusion.</p>"
